title: MagicISO Maker with virtual drive 5.4 Build 255
description:
MagicISO Maker 5.4 Build 255 and Magicdisc   


It can directly create, edit, extract,convert and burn ISO files.

******************************************************************VhmSays******************************************************************************

Install via Setup_MagicISO255.exe, DO NOT run app afterwards!

Copy MagicISO.exe and miso.exe to install directory overwriting originals

Double click on magicISO.reg or import into registry. (Vista users may need to do this as administrator)

To enable virtual drives Install setup_magicdisc.exe 

******************************************************************VhmSays******************************************************************************
